{"id":272434,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-上海维权人士孙洪琴被截访后遭行政拘留/","date":"2013-01-03T18:45:55Z","modified":"2013-01-03T18:45:55Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士孙洪琴被截访后遭行政拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员雷鸣报道）上海维权人士孙洪琴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年元旦下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>时左右，在北京天安门广场乞讨，被天安门分局警察抓住。孙洪琴哀求警察：“我一分钱还没有讨到，我没有饭吃，让我再继续讨吧。”警察对孙洪琴说：“我给你去一个有饭吃的地方。”于是，将孙洪琴带到天安门分局给了她一份写着“生活苦难”等字样的训诫书。随后将她送到马家楼，这个马家楼集中营就是非法关押上访维权人士的黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时，上海驻京办截访人员将孙洪琴接出马家楼黑监狱，又将她转送到北京市接济管理中心（此处也是非法关押访民的黑监狱）继续非法关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日中午</span><span>，上海驻京办截访人员强制把孙洪琴押上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1461</span><span>次列车，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">58</span><span>分离开北京。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时到达上海，闸北区芷江西路派出所警察直接从火车站把孙洪琴带到派出所，没有传唤证，给她做笔录。做完笔录告知她，行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年单位领导污辱孙洪琴的人格尊严，孙洪琴拿起法律的武器保护妇女的权利，她依仗《宪法》、《妇女权益保障法》等相关法律法规向法院提起诉讼，遭到闸北区法院做假材料枉法裁判。上海市长宁区法院从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年至今冻结孙洪琴唯一生活来源——养老金。她在这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>年里靠乞讨度日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年孙洪琴拥有土地使用权的私房又遭到贱价强征，使她不仅衣食无着，更居无定所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>孙洪琴在十多年艰辛困苦的维权路上一直关心和帮助其他权益受到侵犯的人，她不畏惧腐败恶势力的迫害，毅然与其他维权人士一起为上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1060</span><span>户被剥夺公民诉权的家庭向市人大要求维护公民诉权，清除司法不作为。孙洪琴踊跃参加《我要立案、捍卫法律、还我诉权》、《声援冯正虎》、《废除劳教恶法》等公民行动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>孙洪琴因反对腐败，捍卫人权长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>年之久，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年至今连续不断遭到打击报复，加上这次已经第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>次被拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>请媒体和社会各界人士关注</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>孙洪琴电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18939958679</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YHEpq5cZrWs/UOWimFKv7FI/AAAAAAAAYGo/-IMFqWnL8SU/s1600/2012%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%8817%E6%97%A5%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3..JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YHEpq5cZrWs/UOWimFKv7FI/AAAAAAAAYGo/-IMFqWnL8SU/s320/2012%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%8817%E6%97%A5%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3..JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Fs3s9sl7BII/UOWiodaNULI/AAAAAAAAYGw/iGOnr9J0aFQ/s1600/DSCI0534.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"185\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Fs3s9sl7BII/UOWiodaNULI/AAAAAAAAYGw/iGOnr9J0aFQ/s320/DSCI0534.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DJBKe4NXzuA/UOWiqvMt1xI/AAAAAAAAYG4/19AVmAMvuYM/s1600/DSCI0545.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"270\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DJBKe4NXzuA/UOWiqvMt1xI/AAAAAAAAYG4/19AVmAMvuYM/s320/DSCI0545.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FQjxsRaIGz4/UOWisJkm8YI/AAAAAAAAYHA/skThdebher4/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E5%BC%BA%E7%83%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%BA%9F%E9%99%A4%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E6%81%B6%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"205\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-FQjxsRaIGz4/UOWisJkm8YI/AAAAAAAAYHA/skThdebher4/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E5%BC%BA%E7%83%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%BA%9F%E9%99%A4%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E6%81%B6%E6%